  "texts": [
    "Fig. 2 highlights the security problems associated with the IoT and the security requirements.",
    "In this section, various security issues concerning IoT devices are elaborated on.",
    "A list of essential security features that need to be considered includes: Challenges of IoT IoT Security RequirementsConfidentiality• Confidentiality: All data exchanged through IoT communication channels must be heavily encrypted to prevent access by malicious actors.",
    "In addition, no information should be leaked to potential snoopers.",
    "• Data Integrity: To prevent any tampering with data in transit by an unauthorised party, DataIntegrity is an essential component of any large-scale centralised system."
  ]
}